               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat Prayer to drive out the enemy and demons, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት: በእንተ፡ መስደዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ወፀር፡</foreign></summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="26v" facs="002">Fols 1r–26v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer to drive out the enemy and demons, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስደዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ወፀር፡</foreign></title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስደዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ ወፀር። እጸውዕ፡ ስመከ፡ ወእኤምኃከ፡ በተድላ፡ ከመ፡ ይንኰርኩሩ፡ ዘልፈ፡ ለጠፈረ፡ ሰማይ፡ በማዕከላ፡</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
